<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.2.1">
<l>tiṇṇal vīṭu mutaṉmu ḻutumā</l>
<l>yeṇṇiṉ mītiya ṉemperu māyaṉ</l>
<l>maṇṇum viṇṇumel lāmuṭa ṉuṇṭanaṅ</l>
<l>kaṇṇaṉ kaṇṇalla tillaiyōr kaṇṇē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being the whole basis for firm good liberation</l>
<l>he is higher than thought, our great trickster,</l>
<l>our Kṛṣṇa who swallowed all heaven and earth,</l>
<l>apart from his eye, the is no eye.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
